high_descs: Turn around and move to the counter at the far end of the room where the lettuce is.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and then turn left to face the refrigerator.
Chill the lettuce for a moment by putting it in the refrigerator, then remove it from the refrigerator.
Turn around and walk straight towards the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce into the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn right. Move to the counter.
Pick up the lettuce from the center of the counter.
Carry the lettuce and turn around then left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce inside. Shut the door then open it. Take out the lettuce and then shut the door.
Carry the lettuce and turn around to find the sink.
Place the lettuce inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a head of lettuce and place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the wall, hang a right, go to the counter where the lettuce is.
Pick up the lettuce that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, then hang a left and go to the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and close the door, remove the lettuce once it is cold.
Turn around and go to the sink across the room.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the sink.
